{"type": "article", "id": 19692, "title": "“变形金刚”积木", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-25T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125720Ibjng86mSpXGR3eH.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t加拿大设计工作室 Bamloff 推出这一套以变形金刚为灵感的积木，一共 5 种，可以拼成卡车、飞船、甲壳虫、公交车和轮船的模型，然后变身成 15 厘米高的机器人，非常巧妙。每一组是由 15 到 20 块小型积木搭建出来的，不仅适合小朋友智力开发，也是放在办公室的有趣的装饰。单个售价 19 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.indiegogo.com/projects/woobots-transformable-wooden-robot#/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150125YdDZin4vJrfLO1oF.jpg\" width=\"880\" height=\"317\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.36022727\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150127z7Pdhbux8N4V2mlp.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150132Wr54eJ6km9upUCBX.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150138VRaL6Ue1hQo3y84I.gif\" width=\"680\" height=\"383\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}